    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      405.93,
      526.38,
      420.24
    ],
    "text": "Respondent by way of a charge sheet dated 06th September 2019, marked P12(a), and that the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      427.72,
      526.41,
      441.0
    ],
    "text": "Respondents failed to conclude the said inquiry within a reasonable time. The main",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      447.33,
      526.42,
      461.64
    ],
    "text": "contention of the Petitioner is that, although he responded to the charges on 02nd October",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      469.14,
      413.35,
      482.42
    ],
    "text": "2019, the disciplinary proceedings were not concluded expeditiously.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      496.79,
      526.34,
      511.1
    ],
    "text": "The 1st Respondent denies the material averments of the Petitioner and states that the inquiry",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      518.46,
      526.12,
      531.74
    ],
    "text": "process has been concluded. It is also stated that the matter is presently pending consideration",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      539.22,
      525.98,
      552.5
    ],
    "text": "by the Hon. Attorney General for further action in terms of Section 15(2) of the Buddhist",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      559.86,
      526.09,
      573.14
    ],
    "text": "Temporalities Ordinance. In these circumstances, the Respondents contend that the present",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      580.62,
      526.03,
      593.9
    ],
    "text": "application is misconceived, and devoid of merit, and that the Petitioner is not entitled to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      601.26,
      350.11,
      614.54
    ],
    "text": "relief in the exercise of the writ jurisdiction of this Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      658.77,
      201.53,
      672.05
    ],
    "text": "Issues for Determination",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      687.45,
      526.03,
      700.73
    ],
    "text": "The matters that arise for determination in this application are whether the Petitioner is",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      707.06,
      526.27,
      721.37
    ],
    "text": "entitled to a writ of mandamus compelling the 1st Respondent to conclude the inquiry and",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      728.85,
      526.08,
      742.13
    ],
    "text": "communicate its decision, whether such relief has become futile in view of the admitted",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      294.65,
      758.5,
      303.48,
      770.5
    ],
    "text": "4",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      72.47,
      526.18,
      85.75
    ],
    "text": "completion of the inquiry, and whether the alternative relief seeking reinstatement is capable",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      93.13,
      188.54,
      106.41
    ],
    "text": "of being granted in law.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      150.61,
      118.34,
      163.89
    ],
    "text": "Analysis",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      178.26,
      526.42,
      192.57
    ],
    "text": "The principal relief sought by the Petitioner is a writ of mandamus compelling the 1st",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      198.9,
      526.42,
      213.21
    ],
    "text": "Respondent to conclude the inquiry initiated by the charge sheet dated 06th September 2019.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      220.69,
      526.21,
      233.97
    ],
    "text": "It is well-settled law that a writ of mandamus will issue only to compel the performance of a",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      241.33,
      526.1,
      254.61
    ],
    "text": "subsisting public duty. Where the duty sought to be enforced has already been performed,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      262.09,
      525.98,
      275.37
    ],
    "text": "such a writ will not lie. In the present case, it is the admitted position that the inquiry has",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      282.76,
      526.07,
      296.04
    ],
    "text": "already been concluded and that the matter is presently under consideration by the Hon.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      303.52,
      526.04,
      316.8
    ],
    "text": "Attorney General. In such circumstances, the principal relief sought by the Petitioner has",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      324.16,
      526.31,
      337.44
    ],
    "text": "been overtaken by events and is incapable of being granted. Mandamus does not lie to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      344.92,
      526.34,
      358.2
    ],
    "text": "compel the performance of an act which has already been performed or is no longer",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      365.56,
      123.86,
      378.84
    ],
    "text": "necessary.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      394.24,
      526.09,
      407.52
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner, in the alternative, seeks reinstatement to the office of Basnayake Nilame.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      415.0,
      526.08,
      428.28
    ],
    "text": "However, it is evident that the term of office in question has already lapsed. In such",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      435.64,
      526.07,
      448.92
    ],
    "text": "circumstances, even assuming that the Petitioner establishes any alleged illegality, this Court",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      456.42,
      526.03,
      469.7
    ],
    "text": "is not in a position to grant the said relief, as no subsisting legal right remains capable of",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      477.06,
      526.2,
      490.34
    ],
