    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      497.82,
      100.7,
      511.1
    ],
    "text": "exist.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      526.5,
      526.07,
      539.78
    ],
    "text": "It is also to be noted that the reliefs sought by the Petitioner are internally inconsistent,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      547.26,
      526.03,
      560.54
    ],
    "text": "inasmuch as the Petitioner seeks both the conclusion of the inquiry and, in the alternative,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      567.9,
      526.14,
      581.18
    ],
    "text": "reinstatement to office. Such reliefs proceed on mutually incompatible premises and further",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      588.54,
      333.31,
      601.82
    ],
    "text": "underscore the untenability of the present application.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      617.34,
      526.22,
      630.62
    ],
    "text": "In the totality of circumstances, the principal relief sought by the Petitioner has become futile,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      637.98,
      526.37,
      651.26
    ],
    "text": "the alternative relief is incapable of being granted, and disentitles the Petitioner to relief in the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      658.77,
      334.99,
      672.05
    ],
    "text": "exercise of the discretionary jurisdiction of this Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      294.65,
      758.5,
      303.48,
      770.5
    ],
    "text": "5",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      72.47,
      189.74,
      85.75
    ],
    "text": "Conclusion and Order",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      101.17,
      526.1,
      114.45
    ],
    "text": "For the foregoing reasons, this Court is of the view that the present application is",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      121.93,
      431.59,
      135.21
    ],
    "text": "misconceived in law, devoid of merit, and has in any event become futile.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      150.61,
      281.33,
      163.89
    ],
    "text": "Accordingly, this application is dismissed.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      179.29,
      526.41,
      192.57
    ],
    "text": "Considering the aforementioned circumstances, the Petitioner is ordered to pay Rs. 10,000 to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      199.93,
      219.05,
      213.21
    ],
    "text": "the State as costs of litigation.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
